y the hotel is well within the capability of hotel management to deal with. Management of the hotel showed an uncaring attitude that is in hindsight evident in many of the other reviews.I doubt the bed bug problem would be noticed in a short stay, as most guests would simply assume some insect bite them at some time, and would not be able to track it back to the hotel.My experience tips the balance of mixed reviews well to the negative side. Travellers are advised to stay away - there are better hotels in the area with equivalent or better rates.	
